         intltool,
         libtool,
         pkg-config,
         ${misc:Depends},
Description: common scripts and macros to develop with MATE
 kosmos-common is an extension to autoconf, automake and libtool for the MATE
 environment and MATE using applications. Included are kosmos-autogen.sh and
 several macros to help in MATE source trees.
